replies.msg:
Martinelli on Emery and Arteta: &quot;Both are amazing people. Unai helped me a lot, he was the first who trusted me and placed me in the team. I will always be very grateful. He was the one who gave me the first minutes in Europe.&quot;<br />
<br />
Martinelli on reports that Real Madrid made an offer for him: &quot;No, nothing has come to me. I am focused here doing my job at Arsenal and my head is here.&quot;

Rivaldo on Mar&iacute;: &quot;I think Pablo Mari will fit in very well at Arsenal &amp; in the Premier League. He's a good player that struggled to impose himself in Europe as a loaned player of Man City for a while, but he really convinced people being part of a great Flamengo team last season&quot;<br />
<br />
Rivaldo: &quot;He is very complete as a defender - capable of bringing the ball forward &amp; a threat on set pieces. He has good passing skills &amp; I liked what I saw from him. In Brazil everyone has good opinion about him &amp; he could be a very successful option for #Arsenal &amp; Mikel Arteta&quot;

